                <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample2">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingOne">
                            <h4 class="mb-0" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne_1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                What is Salesforce, and how can it benefit your company?
                            </h4>
                        </div>

                        <div id="collapseOne_1" class="collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                    Salesforce is a platform for Customer Relationship Management (CRM), which helps
                                    companies manage and automate their sales, customer service, and marketing
                                    processes. It can benefit your business by providing a centralized location for
                                    customer data, allowing you to understand better and communicate with your customers
                                    and streamlining your sales and marketing efforts.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingTwo">
                            <h4 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo_2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                What services do we offer as a Salesforce partner?
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseTwo_2" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                    Our services include Salesforce implementation, customization, integration, and
                                    support. We also provide training and ongoing support to help ensure that your
                                    company is getting the most out of Salesforce.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingFour">
                            <h4 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree_3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                What is Salesforce Implementation, and how can it benefit your company?
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseThree_3" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                    Salesforce Implementation is the process of setting up and customizing Salesforce
                                    specifically for your business. It includes tasks like transferring data, tailoring
                                    the system, integrating with other tools, and training your team. By implementing
                                    Salesforce, you can boost efficiency, skyrocket productivity, and gain invaluable
                                    insights into your operations.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingFive">
                            <h4 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour_4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                How can Suyati revolutionize your business with Salesforce Marketing Cloud?
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseFour_4" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                    At Suyati, we're experts in Salesforce Marketing Cloud, and we're here to
                                    revolutionize your business. We'll help you strategize and plan, implement and
                                    deploy, train and support, and analyze your data with Salesforce Marketing Cloud.
                                    Our mission is to maximize the potential of your Salesforce Marketing Cloud solution
                                    and drive remarkable results for your business.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-header" id="headingFive">
                            <h4 class="mb-0 collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive_5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                What can Suyati do as your trusted Salesforce partner for Communities?
                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseFive_5" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>
                                    As a trusted Salesforce partner, Suyati offers a range of services to help you make
                                    the most of Salesforce Communities. We'll customize and set up your community,
                                    integrate it seamlessly, provide comprehensive training and ongoing support, and
                                    optimize it for continued success. With Suyati by your side, your Salesforce
                                    Communities will thrive.
